DocumentType.docDescriptionT3: A more detailed description of the works, with an indication of the use of materials or quality indication, so that the expert is able to form an image of the quality of the building.
DocumentType.docDescriptionT4: A detailed description of the works, specifying the type, size(volume or surface), use of materials, quality designation  if applicable, ...to allow the expert to get an idea of the size and quality of the renovation.
DocumentType.docElectricity: Certificate of conformity of electrical installation
DocumentType.docEstimation: If not yet defined: an estimate showing the cost for each item of the construction and specifying the type(contractor costs or purchase of equipment for own work) and VAT.
DocumentType.docEstimationProf: An estimate of the cost of works drawn up by a professional(builder or architect) or equivalent, stating the cost per item of the construction, specifying the type(contractor costs or purchase of equipment for own work) and the VAT.
DocumentType.docEstimationTurnkey: A more detailed description of the works, with an indication of the use of materials or quality indication, and the price of the works drawn up by a professional(developer or architect) or equivalent, including any acquired options(eg expensive kitchen, higher level of finish, ...) with the cost and, where applicable, indicating the works executed by the owner(purchase of equipment for own work).Clear indication of whether VAT is included or not.
DocumentType.docEstimationUnknownWorks: An estimate showing the cost for each item of the construction and specifying the type(contractor costs or purchase of equipment for own work) and VAT.Is the budget of the works more than 75.000 euro ? Then the list should be drawn up by a professional, such as an architect or a contractor.
DocumentType.docLandplot: Surface of the plot and / or plan of the site(not needed for an apartment without a garden)
DocumentType.docLandplotT1: Surface of the plot and / or plan of the site
DocumentType.docPlanFuture: A plan or draft of the design
DocumentType.docPlanFutureUnknownWorks: Will the works change the volume or division or the building ? Then a plan or draft of the design is also needed.
DocumentType.docUnknownNewBuildTypeT3: In case of a built to order project(with your own architect and one or more contractors): A more detailed description of the works, with an indication of the use of materials or quality indication, so that the expert is able to form an image of the quality of the building + an estimate of the cost of works drawn up by a professional(builder or architect) or equivalent, stating the cost per item of the construction, specifying the type(contractor costs or purchase of equipment for own work) and the VAT.
DocumentType.docUnknownNewBuildTypeTurnkey: In case of a turnkey project: A more detailed description of the works, with an indication of the use of materials or quality indication, and the price of the works drawn up by a professional(developer or architect) or equivalent, including any acquired options(eg more expensive kitchen, higher level of finish, ...) with the cost and, where applicable, indicating the works executed by the owner(purchase of building materials for own work).Clear indication of whether VAT is included or not.
